{"tid":1621661,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"如果邊間公司因商場唔開而扣假扣鐘就永遠罷買罷食","createTime":"2019-10-04T14:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T07:14:12.000Z","uid":193504,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8fc7f5fec134227d8feabef4c2da0bba4c947e","tid":1621661,"uid":193504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"好多普通市民會覺得因為示威活動<br />\n而令到佢地返唔到工，被無理扣鐘扣假！<br />\n<br />\n有好多刻薄既公司唔理佢地生命安全，<br />\n扣鐘扣假等行為...從而令班和理非市民就會覺得受影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然民意係現況唔再重要，<br />\n但其實我地都可以幫下一班黃色上班族<br />\n施壓力俾啲扣鐘扣假既冷血公司！<br />\n<br />\n有更多假先可以令佢地係有需要時請假！<br />\n假如用黎遊行或罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重申一次：六大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"1e7ebef40fea65bc3b80fd4baa18e86426282dac","tid":1621661,"uid":22500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330486e054948758e9809220ca9e54a77b338286","tid":1621661,"uid":229377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:23:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n好多零售都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d888316df8d7cb6a2b742ba6493451d5f18cd846","tid":1621661,"uid":167128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"推阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}